{"title":"Wahoo’s End of Tour Flash Sale has Trainers & Accessories on Sale (and in Stock)","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/19/wahoo-end-of-tour-flash-sale/","date":1626718305000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Already going through Tour withdrawal? Can’t wait to work on those FTP numbers on&nbsp;<em>your </em>schedule?&nbsp;Wahoo gets it <span>— with <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/08/11/wahoo-kickr-smart-trainers-get-tilting-axis-feet-for-natural-rocking-motion-and-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wahoo trainers</a> back in stock and on sale until Tuesday, y</span>ou can level up your pain cave.</p><p>The brand <a href=\"https://www.wahoofitness.com/devices?rfsn=4091298.de5aa\">announced a flash sale today</a> to celebrate the end of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/15/insider-10-questions-for-a-tour-de-france-performance-coach/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tour de France</a>. It’s a bit of an exceptional event for Wahoo, which typically doesn’t slash its prices. But it’s a hell of a way to re-introduce its entire range of indoor trainers, which had spent a prolonged stint under the out-of-stock label like many products this year.</p><p>Act fast if you’re interested: the price drop ends at 11:59 PM EDT on Tuesday, July 20.</p><p><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Wahoo-Kickr-Climb-adjusts-angle-to-simulate-climbing-w-indoor-trainer-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Wahoo-Kickr-Climb-adjusts-angle-to-simulate-climbing-w-indoor-trainer-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x336/rscb25/ng:webp/ngcb25\" alt=\"Wahoo Kickr Climb\" width=\"1200\" height=\"833\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Wahoo-Kickr-Climb-adjusts-angle-to-simulate-climbing-w-indoor-trainer-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x336/rscb25/ng:webp/ngcb25\" ezoid=\"0.9896015232667186\"></a></p><h2>Wahoo’s Trainer Primacy</h2><p>Wahoo’s indoor trainers compete strongly for the industry lead with their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/09/best-indoor-bike-trainers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">comprehensive performance, capable app, and competitive price points</a>. Other strong points include quick response to programming changes, measurement accuracy, and quiet operation. Riders tend to enjoy Wahoo’s connectivity and easy-to-use display <span>— that and the acute joy of physical agony.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p>Riding indoors can be “as fun as playing video games,” Wahoo says. Fun? Sure, as long as you enjoy suffering<span>. Wahoo makes it cheaper than ever to load out your pain cave with the best trainers in the business.</span></p><p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Wahoo-Kickr-Bike-trainer_connected-smart-indoor-training-fitness-bike_motor-brake.jpg\" alt=\"Wahoo Kickr Bike trainer, connected smart indoor training fitness bike\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Wahoo-Kickr-Bike-trainer_connected-smart-indoor-training-fitness-bike_motor-brake.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Wahoo-Kickr-Bike-trainer_connected-smart-indoor-training-fitness-bike_motor-brake-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Wahoo-Kickr-Bike-trainer_connected-smart-indoor-training-fitness-bike_motor-brake-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Wahoo-Kickr-Bike-trainer_connected-smart-indoor-training-fitness-bike_motor-brake-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Wahoo-Kickr-Bike-trainer_connected-smart-indoor-training-fitness-bike_motor-brake-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Wahoo-Kickr-Bike-trainer_connected-smart-indoor-training-fitness-bike_motor-brake-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Wahoo-Kickr-Bike-trainer_connected-smart-indo